Resources expended in supporting efforts such as <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">community</ENAMEX> legal
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">education</ENAMEX>, outreach, state planning and resource development also
would not be factored into the program's "cost-per-case."
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LSC</ENAMEX> is carefully studying how to refine the "cost-per-case"
